flowRoot.flowPara: Philippine education system dropout and survival rates, 2013-2015

1. Dropout rates are computed based on the national-level cohort. Any inconsistencies in the data would be due to international immigration, failing students, and the movement into and out of the private education system.
2. Each line should not be interpreted as a single cohort. Rather, the lines reflect the movements across each cohort present during that particular year.
